        "TileImage": "$($repository 453f7e3d-5c85-4cdc-8fc0-af921679a5e2).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47, we are back at the Dartmoor Mansion. It has recently been bought by the Carlise family. We were suspicious about this sudden renting after our last mission so we did background checks on everyone working for the house.\r\rTurns out 2 people have been arrested for smuggling weed. Turns out the weed is the same one from the Garden Show. These two people; Ruben Doyle and Amelia Reid might be apart of the plant stealing business from your last mission. You must take care of them.",
